data.description: **Potential to purchase two corner buildings for major corner expansion-- Neighboring building also for sale SEE DCDC2088448** THREE VACANT units--Uniquely located  4 unit building in Carver Langston.  Set atop a hill with beautiful views, the building promises fantastic returns .   The vacant lot located at the left of the building is included in the sale.  This offers tremendous potential for a developer-- there are multiple avenues for expanding the building up and out!  Neighboring lots currently have 13 unit buildings and 11 unit buildings under construction!All this within a  short walk to  public transportation and all of the entertainment, shopping and dining on H ST via the H St Trolley stop at 19th. Don't miss this one!
